00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.129
Oh, it's like sticky like mud.

00:04:53.129 --> 00:04:54.304
And we are done.

00:04:54.304 --> 00:04:55.981
You can grab a spoon

00:04:55.981 --> 00:04:59.648
and just look at this
beautiful curry paste.

00:05:02.354 --> 00:05:04.939
There are few things in this world

00:05:04.939 --> 00:05:07.054
that make you feel as accomplished

00:05:07.054 --> 00:05:10.720
and as successful as finishing
pounding a curry paste.

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:13.894
It's right up there with
winning a gold medal.

