00:05:32.607 --> 00:05:35.024
So first put that into a pot.

00:05:36.780 --> 00:05:37.613
And then add water.

00:05:37.613 --> 00:05:38.601
And as you add that water,

00:05:38.601 --> 00:05:40.338
just sort of mix it.

00:05:40.338 --> 00:05:42.167
Mix it into that curry paste.

00:05:42.167 --> 00:05:46.033
Make sure that curry paste
dissolves into the water.

00:05:46.033 --> 00:05:48.690
Oh that aroma is just ridiculous.

00:05:48.690 --> 00:05:51.729
Now we're gonna move over
to the street food cart

00:05:51.729 --> 00:05:53.749
to the street food recipe cart.

