smell that citrusy aroma.

00:06:52.076 --> 00:06:53.226
These are gonna go into the curry

00:06:53.226 --> 00:06:55.091
to provide a nice fragrance

00:06:55.091 --> 00:06:58.174
and also to take away the meaty aroma

00:06:59.421 --> 00:07:00.421
